  "instructions": [
    "1. Cut the tofu into small cubes and coat with cumin and chili powder.",
    "2. Heat a skillet over medium-high heat and cook the tofu until crispy.",
    "3. Meanwhile, prepare the avgolemono slaw by mixing the store-bought or homemade avgolemono with lime juice.",
    "4. Warm the corn tortillas by wrapping them in a damp paper towel and microwaving for 20-30 seconds.",
    "5. Assemble the tacos by placing the cooked tofu onto a tortilla, followed by a spoonful of avgolemono slaw and any desired toppings.",
